sql.statement: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Exercises ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, DayName VARCHAR(50), DayID INTERGER, ExerName VARCHAR(50), Type INTERGER)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Days ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, DayNum INTERGER, DayName VARCHAR(50), DayID INTERGER, Type INTERGER, PhaseID INTERGER, StrengthID INTERGER, HasRipper INTERGER, LastDate VARCHAR(50), Completions INTERGER)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Phases ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, Name VARCHAR(50), Weeks VARCHAR(50), PhaseID INTERGER, Completions INTERGER)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Strength ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, dayID INTEGER, Name VARCHAR(50), Weeks VARCHAR(50), StrengthID INTEGER, Type INTEGER Completions INTEGER)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Results ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, profile VARCHAR(50), ExerciseName VARCHAR(50), weight INTERGER, reps INTERGER, band VARCHAR(50), time VARCHAR(50), assist VARCHAR(50), date VARCHAR(50), notes VARCHAR(100))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Weighin ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, profile VARCHAR(50), weight INTERGER, date VARCHAR(50))
